{"tid":1678571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4個幾月的反思需要","createTime":"2019-10-27T17:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:48:43.000Z","uid":82593,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"01aeb9e58b371804b5675117410797ea4fc7d43c","tid":1678571,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:17:02.000Z","msg":"抗爭左成4個幾月，初初好聚到人，但漸漸都活動越多，好多人已經冇哂目標咁抗爭，加返黑警黨鐵政府連成一線之後，而家真係死既死，傷既傷。<br />\n<br />\n我想大家今晚休息之餘停低諗諗：<br />\n<br />\n1.既然我地好清楚香港人係升級唔到（事實要升一早升左），咁可唔可以嘗試打返我地最擅長的經濟戰，起底戰，暫時以最少的傷亡去保持大家抗爭的心？<br />\n<br />\n2.班狗而家就一定唔會留手，出擊同遊行係需要，但近日會發現一個區聚集會令送頭人士增加，在保護大家可以盡可能安全之下，多區開花會否更好的選擇，時間亦是否需要有變動？而遊行係咪應該全交返俾和理非負責？<br />\n<br />\n3. 文宣連儂牆的打壓，已經進入更嚴重的階段，既然連儂牆手足開始俾狗捉，我地貼文宣是否應只在早上同放工時間進行？ 另外，Airdrop 文宣又可唔可夾定一班幾個咁一齊做？（同事們或者同學們）<br />\n<br />\n4. 區議會的選情會係第一張正式的民意成績表，我地文宣的方向，除左將抗爭事情記錄，是否可以開始集中18區建制議員的惡行，將各區的議員及其政黨做過的惡行都文宣去該區？<br />\n<br />\n5.遊行的次數多又是否利多於弊？遊行的主題同人物又是否可以更需要考慮，遊行是否可以將香港不同界別的人士去以獲得更大回響，如先前的醫護界，法律界，信仰派，什至香港的少數族裔？在黎緊，我地又有冇可能將海關，消防，入境的三大紀律部隊，都舉行到一次專屬遊行？<br />\n<br />\n我並唔代表每一位手足的想法，我雖然出過前線，但亦都冇資格批評每一位手足的行動，我只希望提醒一下大家，在明知香港人升級唔到的情況下，在明知黑警黨鐵政府的連線下，在手足越黎越多傷亡被捕的情況下，會唔會需要改變？<br />\n<br />\n要插要屌，請輕力點。"},{"pid":"2a679368282a652a9fc93149a5cf9291986de3db","tid":1678571,"uid":318427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:24:59.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"f37e2adc6f5b2a17db5d319915a9329b5b581950","tid":1678571,"uid":167277,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"活動太多 要集中 <br />\n琴日又醫護集會 今日又尖沙咀<br />\n好難聚人, 集中宣傳1星期1個就夠<br />\n<br />\n文宣要快閃 或者全民文宣組 每人貼少少<br />\n<br />\n18區開花就太散 好似8月5咁, 7區就差唔多"},{"pid":"7a6e5a9f41a788a7d525873a123d5dc06bcb2cbd","tid":1678571,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7895127dcb983ab23ced06ac3631b3b65203b111","tid":1678571,"uid":55144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a716df4d90fe46aef9299e4af4a22f1765aa08b6","tid":1678571,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8a73445d9376ffb2479b1172dd7feea904dc5c5f","tid":1678571,"uid":36199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"b0aba97815bf879a63afa559d2e8560e53962fa5","tid":1678571,"uid":323113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:56:11.000Z","msg":"同意，集中d會好d<br />\n活動太多，大家會參加左一日，<br />\n然後第二日會累或懶左唔想出"},{"pid":"05314ba013d8d18066e6229c0d077970da9523c5","tid":1678571,"uid":170297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:57:34.000Z","msg":"每月3小搞 1大搞"},{"pid":"fdaf3b703843c2ab63d2230cc04338252c0027a5","tid":1678571,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:58:11.000Z","msg":"關於文宣<br />\n希望大家以後出席和理活動時，每人都印少少文宣派比身邊嘅人，少極都喺公司學校印幾張<br />\n利用每次相對安全又聚到人嘅時間做宣傳（而家就咁嗌幾月幾邊度見，冇活動詳情，如果一開始唔知有活動嘅聽完都無用）"},{"pid":"8a340f404b3d55709f04e054244eeb6f4dbf55e6","tid":1678571,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:59:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a412cc9a81cdf7e6f36ecc8c2c614f11254e5a8","tid":1678571,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"其實反送中暫緩後 目標模糊<br />\n五大訴求 都少咗提"},{"pid":"855c84a6b0682edacd617f6e8fc7d6dfc7146be0","tid":1678571,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7895127dcb983ab23ced06ac3631b3b65203b111","tid":1678571,"uid":55144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1991383ca731f8e37e437822c13641e199572522","tid":1678571,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:00:38.000Z","msg":"每星期一遊行一集會 我覺得點都要繼續<br />\n有人出黎先聚到人氣 有人氣先有士氣<br />\n冇野搞 運動就容易不了了之"},{"pid":"7b9897ed30ce3aa6b3ea763cc3418b1768dc3752","tid":1678571,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"決心問題"},{"pid":"17ffd978fb593d39bbb71c64fd6ea238212c11b3","tid":1678571,"uid":26344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"「失蹤人口」今日個尖沙咀集會搞手去左邊？係鬼定手足？（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2cde348af913237106fcc3620463edd909bd8e66","tid":1678571,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:02:06.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f18062c36bbd731253877552360182676bc441","tid":1678571,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"建議7-8區開花就好<br />\n<br />\n其中一區係聚集人（吸引大部分object）<br />\n當確認其中一區引到大量object，咁其他區要用無底線嘅行動回應（e.g.燒狗宿，大規模爆黨鐵站，獵殺落單狗)"},{"pid":"e66344987df6cfd9424bdf71e8652864a20392fc","tid":1678571,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"活動建議一至二星期一個大，平時夾一個小。唔好日日都有好多小活動、最緊要唔好同大活動撞期，大活動為主線"},{"pid":"5471fccbb2cd5dfd66dedfa6ca6318439d4a0706","tid":1678571,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"無左目標係嘅<br />\n區議會宣傳要開始<br />\n我覺得勇武要減少被捕<br />\n最好方法就係真快閃，同埋早啲返屋企<br />\n多區嘅話5-6區效果最好"},{"pid":"2da29c9467c666fb904abfec55c6fb1d04dfae57","tid":1678571,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"任何制度內玩既遊戲都係傷唔到個制度，掌握制度既人先會同你玩。<br />\n唔洗諗區議會有用。"},{"pid":"d17a604ba94d28785c3afb04eea9c44b61b4974b","tid":1678571,"uid":276821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:07:22.000Z","msg":"開花有個問題，要set一個目標死線，每一次都要，唔可能將手足條命白白咁送走，五大訴求外，要有實質目標要求，如831 CCTV，快將兩個月，點解無人再提出?  黨鐵唔回應或者唔交就行動，會唔會比較有用得多"},{"pid":"5ade52496d7a8e05a847fbc3204d87a2342cb248","tid":1678571,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdaf3b703843c2ab63d2230cc04338252c0027a5","tid":1678571,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:58:11.000Z","msg":"關於文宣<br />\n希望大家以後出席和理活動時，每人都印少少文宣派比身邊嘅人，少極都喺公司學校印幾張<br />\n利用每次相對安全又聚到人嘅時間做宣傳（而家就咁嗌幾月幾邊度見，冇活動詳情，如果一開始唔知有活動嘅聽完都無用）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"唔一定要聚到人，自己印自己貼都可以，問題係時間，一定要選人多的時間，所以我提議返工/放工時間，就連8，9點少人時段都可免則免"},{"pid":"75ccfeb00a2deeb6dddd838f64ec27aba21b9e8a","tid":1678571,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a412cc9a81cdf7e6f36ecc8c2c614f11254e5a8","tid":1678571,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"其實反送中暫緩後 目標模糊<br />\n五大訴求 都少咗提"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"政府好成功將目標轉移去班Condom 狗身上，因為暴力畫面永遠最Eye catching"},{"pid":"674d07cab94a4bc424fb2f3dbd3b360c1021560b","tid":1678571,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"香港人冇勇武基因<br />\n學吓智利伊拉克啦"}]}